INSERT INTO `examine_guide` VALUES (1,'Joto la Mwili','<p>Joto la kawaida la mwili linatofautiana kwa karibu 0.5 digrii Celsius wakati wa mchana na inaweza kuwa chini kidogo (mapema asubuhi) au juu kidogo (jioni) kuliko joto la kawaida la mwili lililoorodheshwa kwenye meza ifuatayo. Ili kupima joto la mwili unahitaji kipima joto cha mifugo. Ni ya bei rahisi sana na inaweza kupatikana katika maduka mengi ya wanyama. Ni nyenzo muhimu kwa mfugaji mzito wa mifugo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Joto la kawaida la mwili<br />\r\nMwili unaweza kufanya kazi vizuri tu kwa joto fulani. Mwili wa wanyama hujihifadhi kwa joto la kawaida, ndani ya anuwai ndogo, ili mifumo ifanye kazi vizuri. Joto hili la kawaida la mwili ni tofauti katika aina tofauti za wanyama.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuna njia kadhaa ambazo wanyama hudhibiti joto la mwili:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nywele, sufu, kutembea, kukimbia, kutetemeka na kuchoma nishati katika malisho huufanya mwili uwe na joto.<br />\r\nKutokwa na jasho, kupumua, kujikunja kwenye tope, na kulala kwenye kivuli kunapunguza mwili.<br />\r\nKupima joto la mwili<br />\r\nTunatumia kipima joto kupima joto la mwili. Kitengo cha kipimo ni digrii sentigredi (&deg; C).<br />\r\nJoto la kawaida la mwili wako ni 37 &deg; C.<br />\r\nTunapima joto la mwili wa wanyama kwa kuweka thermometer kwenye mkundu.<br />\r\nKipimajoto<br />\r\nAngalia kipima joto chako. Angalia mstari wa fedha wa zebaki ndani yake na kiwango na nambari zilizowekwa alama kando yake.<br />\r\nKabla ya kuitumia lazima uhakikishe kuwa kiwango cha zebaki iko chini ya 35 &deg; C. Ikiwa sivyo, tikisa kipima joto ili kufanya kiwango kishuke.<br />\r\nKila wakati unapotumia kipima joto kiisafishe na maji baridi na sabuni au upake dawa ya kuua viini baadaye.<br />\r\nUsioshe kipima joto katika maji ya moto kwani hii itaipasua. Usiache kipima joto chako kwenye jua kwani hii inaweza kuipasua. Beba kipima joto katika kesi kwenye mfuko au mfuko wako. Usitumie kipima joto chako cha mifugo kwa watu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"THERMOMETER \" src=\"https://static.vikaspedia.in/media/images_en/agriculture/livestock/thermometertest.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:200px\" title=\"THERMOMETER \" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>Kipimajoto</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><strong>Jinsi ya kuchukua joto la mwili wa wanyama</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nDhibiti mnyama.<br />\r\nHoja mkia upande.<br />\r\nWeka thermometer kwa upole ndani ya mkundu, kwa kadiri iwezekanavyo.<br />\r\nShikilia kipima joto kwa pembe ili iweze kugusa ukuta wa puru. Shika mtego thabiti, ikiwa mnyama anajisaidia haja ndogo au kukohoa kipima joto kinaweza kutoka au kwenda kwenye puru.<br />\r\nShikilia kipima joto kwa nusu dakika. Ikiwa hauna hesabu ya saa polepole hadi 30 (moja, mbili, tatu, ............ thelathini).<br />\r\nOndoa kipima joto na uifute ikiwa ni lazima na uisome. Usiguse balbu kwani hii inaweza kubadilisha usomaji.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"how to\" src=\"https://static.vikaspedia.in/media/images_en/agriculture/livestock/how-totest.jpg\" style=\"height:350px; width:500px\" title=\"how to\" /></p>','<p>Normal body temperature varies by about 0.5 degrees Celsius during the day and can be a bit lower (early morning) or a little bit higher (evening) than the normal body temperatures listed in the following table. To measure body temperature you need a veterinary thermometer. It&nbsp;is very cheap and can be found in most agro-vet shops. It is an essential tool for the serious livestock farmer.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The normal body temperature</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The body can only work properly at a certain temperature. The animal body maintains itself at a constant temperature, within a small range, in order for the systems to work properly. This normal body temperature is different in different types of animals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are a number of ways by which animals control the temperature of the body:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hair, wool, walking, running, shivering and the burning of energy in feed keep the body warm.</li>\r\n	<li>Sweating, panting, wallowing in mud, and lying in the shade cool the body.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Measuring body temperature</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We use a thermometer to measure the temperature of the body. The unit of measurement is degrees centigrade (&deg;C).</li>\r\n	<li>The normal temperature of your body is 37&deg;C.</li>\r\n	<li>We measure the body temperature of animals by placing a thermometer in the anus.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Thermometer</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Look at your thermometer. Notice the silver line of the mercury inside it and the scale with numbers marked along it.</li>\r\n	<li>Before you use it you must make sure that the mercury level is below 35&deg;C. If it is not, shake the thermometer to make the level go down.</li>\r\n	<li>Every time you use the thermometer clean it with cold water and soap or disinfect it afterward.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Do not wash the thermometer in hot water as this will burst it. Do not leave your thermometer in the sun as this may burst it. Carry the thermometer in a case in your pocket or bag. Do not use your veterinary thermometer for people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"THERMOMETER \" src=\"https://static.vikaspedia.in/media/images_en/agriculture/livestock/thermometertest.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:200px\" title=\"THERMOMETER \" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Thermometer</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to take the body temperature of animals</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Control the animal.</li>\r\n	<li>Move the tail to the side.</li>\r\n	<li>Put the thermometer gently into the anus, as far as possible.</li>\r\n	<li>Hold the thermometer at an angle so that it touches the wall of the rectum. Keep a firm grip on the thermometer, if the animal defecates or coughs the thermometer could come out or go into the rectum.</li>\r\n	<li>Hold the thermometer in place for half a minute. If you do not have a watch count slowly up to 30 (one, two, three, ............ thirty).</li>\r\n	<li>Remove the thermometer and wipe it if necessary and read it. Do not touch the bulb as this could change the reading.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"how to\" src=\"https://static.vikaspedia.in/media/images_en/agriculture/livestock/how-totest.jpg\" style=\"height:350px; width:500px\" title=\"how to\" /></p>','<p>Joto la kawaida la mwili linatofautiana kwa karibu 0.5 digrii Celsius wakati wa mchana na inaweza kuwa chini kidogo (mapema asubuhi) au juu kidogo (jioni) kuliko joto la kawaida la mwili lililoorodheshwa kwenye meza ifuatayo. Ili kupima joto la mwili unahitaji kipima joto cha mifugo. Ni ya bei rahisi sana na inaweza kupatikana katika maduka mengi ya wanyama. Ni nyenzo muhimu kwa mfugaji mzito wa mifugo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Joto la kawaida la mwili<br />\r\nMwili unaweza kufanya kazi vizuri tu kwa joto fulani. Mwili wa wanyama hujihifadhi kwa joto la kawaida, ndani ya anuwai ndogo, ili mifumo ifanye kazi vizuri. Joto hili la kawaida la mwili ni tofauti katika aina tofauti za wanyama.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kuna njia kadhaa ambazo wanyama hudhibiti joto la mwili:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nywele, sufu, kutembea, kukimbia, kutetemeka na kuchoma nishati katika malisho huufanya mwili uwe na joto.<br />\r\nKutokwa na jasho, kupumua, kujikunja kwenye tope, na kulala kwenye kivuli kunapunguza mwili.<br />\r\nKupima joto la mwili<br />\r\nTunatumia kipima joto kupima joto la mwili. Kitengo cha kipimo ni digrii sentigredi (&deg; C).<br />\r\nJoto la kawaida la mwili wako ni 37 &deg; C.<br />\r\nTunapima joto la mwili wa wanyama kwa kuweka thermometer kwenye mkundu.<br />\r\nKipimajoto<br />\r\nAngalia kipima joto chako. Angalia mstari wa fedha wa zebaki ndani yake na kiwango na nambari zilizowekwa alama kando yake.<br />\r\nKabla ya kuitumia lazima uhakikishe kuwa kiwango cha zebaki iko chini ya 35 &deg; C. Ikiwa sivyo, tikisa kipima joto ili kufanya kiwango kishuke.<br />\r\nKila wakati unapotumia kipima joto kiisafishe na maji baridi na sabuni au upake dawa ya kuua viini baadaye.<br />\r\nUsioshe kipima joto katika maji ya moto kwani hii itaipasua. Usiache kipima joto chako kwenye jua kwani hii inaweza kuipasua. Beba kipima joto katika kesi kwenye mfuko au mfuko wako. Usitumie kipima joto chako cha mifugo kwa watu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"THERMOMETER \" src=\"https://static.vikaspedia.in/media/images_en/agriculture/livestock/thermometertest.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:200px\" title=\"THERMOMETER \" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>Kipimajoto</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><strong>Jinsi ya kuchukua joto la mwili wa wanyama</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nDhibiti mnyama.<br />\r\nHoja mkia upande.<br />\r\nWeka thermometer kwa upole ndani ya mkundu, kwa kadiri iwezekanavyo.<br />\r\nShikilia kipima joto kwa pembe ili iweze kugusa ukuta wa puru. Shika mtego thabiti, ikiwa mnyama anajisaidia haja ndogo au kukohoa kipima joto kinaweza kutoka au kwenda kwenye puru.<br />\r\nShikilia kipima joto kwa nusu dakika. Ikiwa hauna hesabu ya saa polepole hadi 30 (moja, mbili, tatu, ............ thelathini).<br />\r\nOndoa kipima joto na uifute ikiwa ni lazima na uisome. Usiguse balbu kwani hii inaweza kubadilisha usomaji.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"how to\" src=\"https://static.vikaspedia.in/media/images_en/agriculture/livestock/how-totest.jpg\" style=\"height:350px; width:500px\" title=\"how to\" /></p>','Body Temperature','Joto la Mwili');
