INSERT INTO `firstaniml_front` VALUES (2,'<p>Kuzuia na kudhibiti magonjwa hukua uchumi, huimarisha jamii, na inaboresha afya ya watu walio katika mazingira magumu, haswa vijana na wazee</p>','<ul><li>Ugonjwa unaweza kuelezewa kama kupotoka kuumiza kutoka kwa hali ya kawaida ya kisaikolojia ya kiumbe cha kutosha kutoa ishara wazi, au dalili. Kupotoka kunaweza kuwa mabadiliko dhahiri ya kikaboni kwenye tishu inayounda chombo au usumbufu wa kiutendaji ambao mabadiliko ya kikaboni sio dhahiri. Ukali wa mabadiliko yanayotokea kwenye seli na tishu zilizowekwa chini ya mawakala wenye kuumiza hutegemea unyeti wa tishu inayohusika na hali na mwendo wa wakala. Magonjwa yanaweza kuwa ya kuambukiza au yasiyo ya kuambukiza.</li><li>Maambukizi ya neno, kama inavyoonekana hapo awali, inamaanisha mwingiliano kati ya viumbe hai viwili, vinavyoitwa mwenyeji na vimelea. Maambukizi ni aina ya vimelea, ambayo inaweza kufafanuliwa kama hali ya kuwepo kwa kiumbe kimoja (vimelea) kwa gharama ya mwingine (mwenyeji). Mawakala (kwa mfano, virusi fulani, bakteria, kuvu, protozoa, minyoo, na arthropods) zinazoweza kuzalisha magonjwa ni vimelea vya magonjwa.</li></ul>','<p>Uchunguzi wa kliniki ni sehemu ya kimsingi ya mchakato wa utambuzi wa mifugo. Bila uchunguzi mzuri wa kliniki na utambuzi sahihi, haiwezekani kwamba matibabu, udhibiti, ubashiri, na ustawi wa wanyama utaboreshwa. Kitabu hiki kitasaidia wakulima katika ufahamu wao wa uchunguzi wa kliniki ya wanyama wa shamba na kutenda kama rejea ya haraka kwa wale ambao wanahitajika kuchunguza spishi isiyojulikana.</p>','AFYA YA NG\'OMBE','UTAGUZI WA NG\'OMBE','<p>Preventing and controlling diseases grows economies, bolsters local communities, and improves the health of vulnerable populations, especially the young and elderly</p>','<p>Kuzuia na kudhibiti magonjwa hukua uchumi, huimarisha jamii, na inaboresha afya ya watu walio katika mazingira magumu, haswa vijana na wazee</p>','<ul><li>A disease may be defined as an injurious deviation from a normal physiological state of an organism sufficient to produce overt signs or symptoms. The deviation may be either an obvious organic change in the tissue composing an organ or a functional disturbance whose organic changes are not obvious. The severity of the changes that occur in cells and tissues subjected to injurious agents is dependent upon both the sensitivity of the tissue concerned and the nature and time course of the agent. Diseases may be either infectious or noninfectious.</li><li>The term infection, as observed earlier, implies an interaction between two living organisms, called the host and the parasite. Infection is a type of parasitism, which may be defined as the state of existence of one organism (the parasite) at the expense of another (the host). Agents (e.g., certain viruses, bacteria, fungi, protozoans, worms, and arthropods) capable of producing disease are pathogens.</li></ul>','<ul><li>Ugonjwa unaweza kuelezewa kama kupotoka kuumiza kutoka kwa hali ya kawaida ya kisaikolojia ya kiumbe cha kutosha kutoa ishara wazi, au dalili. Kupotoka kunaweza kuwa mabadiliko dhahiri ya kikaboni kwenye tishu inayounda chombo au usumbufu wa kiutendaji ambao mabadiliko ya kikaboni sio dhahiri. Ukali wa mabadiliko yanayotokea kwenye seli na tishu zilizowekwa chini ya mawakala wenye kuumiza hutegemea unyeti wa tishu inayohusika na hali na mwendo wa wakala. Magonjwa yanaweza kuwa ya kuambukiza au yasiyo ya kuambukiza.</li><li>Maambukizi ya neno, kama inavyoonekana hapo awali, inamaanisha mwingiliano kati ya viumbe hai viwili, vinavyoitwa mwenyeji na vimelea. Maambukizi ni aina ya vimelea, ambayo inaweza kufafanuliwa kama hali ya kuwepo kwa kiumbe kimoja (vimelea) kwa gharama ya mwingine (mwenyeji). Mawakala (kwa mfano, virusi fulani, bakteria, kuvu, protozoa, minyoo, na arthropods) zinazoweza kuzalisha magonjwa ni vimelea vya magonjwa.</li></ul>','CATTLE HEALTH','AFYA YA NG\'OMBE','<p>Clinical examination is a fundamental part of the process of veterinary diagnosis. Without a proficient clinical examination and an accurate diagnosis, it is unlikely that the treatment, control, prognosis, and welfare of animals will be optimized. This book will assist farmers in their understanding of farm animal clinical examination and&nbsp;act as a quick reference for those who are called upon to examine an unfamiliar species.</p>','<p>Uchunguzi wa kliniki ni sehemu ya kimsingi ya mchakato wa utambuzi wa mifugo. Bila uchunguzi mzuri wa kliniki na utambuzi sahihi, haiwezekani kwamba matibabu, udhibiti, ubashiri, na ustawi wa wanyama utaboreshwa. Kitabu hiki kitasaidia wakulima katika ufahamu wao wa uchunguzi wa kliniki ya wanyama wa shamba na kutenda kama rejea ya haraka kwa wale ambao wanahitajika kuchunguza spishi isiyojulikana.</p>','CATTLE EXAMINATIONS','UTAGUZI WA NG\'OMBE');
